A class body contains specification of a set of fields which defines attributes of the objects and a set of methods which defines behaviours of the objects. Class is the unit of modularization in object oriented program. <div>A class is a blueprint which defines the attributes (fields) and behaviours (methods) common to a number of objects.</div><div>A class is a user defined blueprint based on which objects are created.</div><div><br></div><div><span style="color: purple;">Object</span> is a concrete entity with a set of attributes and a set of behaviours.</div><div>Object also have identify, lifetime and scope and belongs to a class.</div><div>Fields defines the attributes of objects instantiated from a class.</div><div>Methods defines the behaviors of objects instantiated from a class.</div><div>Objects maintain state in instance variables (attributes).</div><div>Objects are allocated from the heap and accessed by reference variables.</div><div>Objects communicates with one another by sending and receiving message.</div><div><table style="width: 99%;border-collapse: collapse;border: 1px solid #ccc;margin-top: 10px;margin-bottom: 10px;margin-left: auto;margin-right: auto;"><tbody><tr><td style="border: 1px solid #ccc;padding-top: 8px;padding-bottom: 8px;padding-left: 17px;padding-right: 17px;text-align: center;background-color: #f0f0f0;font-weight: bold;">Definition</td><td style="border: 1px solid #ccc;padding-top: 8px;padding-bottom: 8px;padding-left: 17px;padding-right: 17px;text-align: center;background-color: #f0f0f0;font-weight: bold;">Description</td></tr><tr><td style="border: 1px solid rgb(204, 204, 204); padding: 8px 17px 17px; text-align: justify;">    class Snake {
          Size size;
          Color color;
          Point position;
          void move(Dir dir) {}
          void eat(Food food) {}
    }</td><td style="border: 1px solid rgb(204, 204, 204); padding: 8px 17px 17px; text-align: center;">Defines attributes and behaviours of snakes.
  Behaviours are used to change states.
  State is combination of attributes values.

     Attributes = {size, color, position}
     Behaviours = {move, eat}
     Attributes = Form</td></tr></tbody></table><br></div>
